Package org.apache.jena.datatypes.xsd

Class XSDbinary

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.datatypes.BaseDatatype
      • org.apache.jena.datatypes.xsd.XSDDatatype
        • org.apache.jena.datatypes.xsd.XSDbinary
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RDFDatatype
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    XSDbase64Binary, XSDhexBinary
    public abstract class XSDbinary
extends XSDDatatype
    Root class for XSD datatypes with binary values, xsd:hexBinary and xsd:base64Binary. The binary value is stored as a byte[] in the LiteralLabel.
